These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, ritmeester, tiparillo
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, roller, trike
1. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is the person driving the trike##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Cigar   | montecristo | ritmeester | tiparillo   |
| Transport      | tram    | roller  | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, aconite, sunflower
There 3 different types of food: mango, cauliflower, radish
1. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Flower      | aconite | marigold     | sunflower      |
| Food   | cauliflower | mango | radish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, pakistani, american
3 different pets are kept: goat, rat, rabbit
1. the pakistani is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the american is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the turkish is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Nationality   | turkish | american  | pakistani       |
| Pet       | goat     | rat | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, snowmobile, quad-bike
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, chaman, baccarat
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Transport    | quad-bike    | snowmobile     | trike |
| Cigar   | baccarat | alhambra | chaman     |

