.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, cain, baccarat
There 3 different types of food: papaya, spinach, avocado
1. the person eating spinach is the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
4. the swisher-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Cigar         | cain | swisher     | baccarat |
| Food   | avocado        | papaya | spinach    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, classical, funk
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, apricot, ebony
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
2. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
3. the fan of funk is the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre        | funk | soul      | classical  |
| Color   | amber       | apricot | ebony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, skateboard, helicopter
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, december, june
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Transport   | helicopter      | motorbike     | skateboard    |
| Birthday           | august | june | december |

