.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, ferret, cat
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, chaman, vegafina
1. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
3. the owner of the ferret is the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Pet    | cat | goat | ferret      |
| Cigar   | dannemann     | vegafina | chaman |

