.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, librarian, coach
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, western, scientific
1. the person watching time-travel movies is the librarian##1
2. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
3. the librarian is on the right of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Job   | coach | librarian | doctor  |
| Movie-Genre     | scientific     | time-travel      | western |

