.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-12::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, skiing, snowboarding
House: cape-cod, palace, ranch-style
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
3. the palace house is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Sport   | snowboarding    | biathlon     | skiing   |
| House   | palace | cape-cod | ranch-style |

