.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, pony
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, gardening, board-games
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Pet      | bird  | pony | chinchilla  |
| Hobby   | gardening | board-games   | sudoku |

