2. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | house | dubstep    |
| Movie-Genre        | zombie    | satire | adventure |

