.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, video-games, collecting
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, baseball, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Hobby           | video-games | collecting | rock-climbing |
| Sport   | cricket  | volleyball      | baseball |

