.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, aconite, orchid
1. the person who growsaconite is in the middle##1
2. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Transport    | roller | car       | jet-ski  |
| Flower   | orchid  | aconite | balloon-flower |

 